The following TLA+ tools are available in this distribtion:

 1) The Syntactic Analyzer: A parser and syntax checker for TLA+
    specifications.

 2) TLC: A model checker and simulator for a subclass of "executable"
    TLA+ specifications.

 3) TLATeX: A program for typesetting TLA+ specifications.   

 4) Beta test versions of 1-3 for the TLA+2 language

 5) The PlusCal translator

For instruction to install and run the tools, please go to

   http://research.microsoft.com/users/lamport/tla/tools.html
